EQ7kNvgHzHCl-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBD-R6Qyoc4p5Qbr9PJsW9L1tTyufr4KQdfJc5NiXmdZg&oe=66F7EA98"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover image.png", "id": "117521453594753", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974535_117521456928086_99350484779883293_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YXVR15OMUfAQ7kNvgE3HMSE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYClIeXFQtbXtG0iUHwvpoXiSWbCvWPyFtGshkZ2RIHfDw&oe=66F7E4CC"}, "display_name": "SENTIO VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "SENTIO VR is the preferred 3D visualization platform for professionals working in the Architecture, Engineering & Construction Industry in 100+ countries. How does a project that has not yet been built look like? Instead of reviewing 2D floorplans, renders & video walkthroughs - SENTIO VR customers put on an Oculus Quest headset for real-time feedback with clients, improved designs & win new projects.\n\nHere are the key features that make SENTIO VR stand out:\n\n1) Plugins for SketchUp & Autodesk Revit\n- No downloads or upload of files needed. Works with your existing design tools\n\n2) No additional downloads\n- No additional PC software is required to manage the model upload process. \n\n3) Intuitive VR meetings\n- Multi-user collaboration meetings have never been easier using access codes & passwords\n\nHave questions? Reach out to us at hello@sentiovr.com", "short_description": "Want to view a construction project before it's built? With SENTIO VR, multiple stakeholders in a project can meet virtually, voice-chat & collaborate over a 3D model enabling better decisions.\n\nSupports SketchUp, Revit & 360 panoramas.\n\nNeed some inspiration? Explore a unique collection of 360 experiences of architectural spaces curated by ArchDaily & our content team.\n\nNote: \n-Permission for Microphone is needed for VR meetings\n-Permission for Device files is needed for downloading 3D models"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_p